00:51:09.607 --> 00:51:10.404
Hej.

613
00:51:13.720 --> 00:51:16.972
Ja sam iz Sanduskog, ok?

614
00:51:18.834 --> 00:51:21.576
Odrastao za Erie.

615
00:51:23.372 --> 00:51:24.361
Niko...

616
00:51:25.440 --> 00:51:28.834
zvaće me zlim...

617
00:51:31.112 --> 00:51:32.415
ni ti...

618
00:51:34.325 --> 00:51:35.357
ser.

619
00:51:37.762 --> 00:51:39.872
To je jezero, Keaney.

620
00:51:41.038 --> 00:51:42.242
Ne računa se.

621
00:51:45.732 --> 00:51:48.008
Nisi li iz Mississippija?

622
00:51:50.039 --> 00:51:52.069
A?
Rečni dječak.


623
00:51:52.104 --> 00:51:55.874
Dođavola, ne.
Ja sam sa Havaja.


624
00:51:57.209 --> 00:51:59.213
I vi ste takvi,
ako bilo ko pita.


625
00:52:00.124 --> 00:52:01.131
Da.

626
00:52:03.647 --> 00:52:07.264
Pa... aloha.

627
00:52:11.802 --> 00:52:12.985
To je duh.

628
00:52:15.333 --> 00:52:16.700
Sad, gdje smo bili?

